        <text class="text_big text__font_colizeum text__color_yellow hero__title-line">COLIZEUM MADRID</text>
      </view>
      <text class="text_middle text__color_white hero__description">
        <text class="text__font_colizeum text__color_yellow">COLIZEUM MADRID</text>
          是一家拥有顶级设备的电竞俱乐部，满足现代电子游戏的所有要求
      </text>
      <view class="hero__book-container">
        <button class="button__book" open-type="contact">预订</button>
        <image class="hero__text-container-decor" src="/assets/3c6e733f074223a6474d.png" mode="widthFix" />
      </view>
    </view>
    <image class="hero__img" src="/assets/795482530f3897564e0c.png" mode="widthFix" />
  </view>
  
